<div class="solution-begin"><span id='sol-start-14' class="fa fa-hand-o-right solution-icon clickable" onclick="toggle_visibility('sol-body-14', 'sol-start-14')">  Solution </span></div><div class="solution-body" id = "sol-body-14" style="display: none;">



